      <title>纽约起诉预借现金提供商 Yellowstone，索赔 14 亿美元，指控其掠夺性贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/new-york-sues-cash-advance-provider-yellowstone-14-billion-alleges-predatory-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，纽约总检察长利蒂蒂亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 起诉现金垫款提供商黄石资本 (Yellowstone Capital)，要求赔偿 14 亿美元，称该公司开展大规模掠夺性贷款业务，对欺诈性贷款收取“天价”利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/new-york-sues-cash-advance-provider-yellowstone-14-billion-alleges-predatory-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 20:54:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
