      <title>零售商 Cencosud 因阿根廷通货膨胀和消费放缓而利润下降 42%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailer-cencosud-posts-profit-down-42-argentine-inflation-slow-consumption-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲最大的零售商之一智利 Cencosud 周二报告称，第四季度净利润下降 42%，降至 833 亿比索（9,400 万美元），而收入则缩水 16% 至 3.30 万亿比索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailer-cencosud-posts-profit-down-42-argentine-inflation-slow-consumption-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 20:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
